page.title: 11HOUSING
page.content: Victoria St,Union St,Edward St,Houghton Rd and Douglas Crescent semi_ detatched or terraced homes with small gardens,Northfields have the same with large gardens, built for the A.C.Delco workers. Winfield St, Ashton Rd, North View, Maidenbower Ave, Beecroft Way, Beech Green and Clifton Rd are semi_detatched with large gardens. Waterlow Rd, Stuart St, Edward St and Olma Rd are terraced with small gardens. Westfield Rd and Capron Rd are flats,semi_detatched and terraced. Regent St is terraced,semi's and detatched. Sunderland are all flats. Chiltern Rd are town houses: detatched, semi's and flats. High St North is mostly 3 storey terraced with basements.
